Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait' before transitioning to 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Median duration of 'Accepted + Wait' across all cases

Name: Longest duration of 'Accepted + Wait' before any subsequent activity

Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average duration difference between 'Accepted + Wait' and 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + Wait' to 'Completed + Closed' across variants
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Total duration from 'Accepted + Wait' to 'Accepted + Assigned' in the most frequent variant
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'begin': "activity == 'Accepted + Wait'", 'end': "activity == 'Completed + Resolved' or activity == 'Completed + Closed' or activity == 'Completed + Cancelled'", 'aggregation': 'minimum'}

Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'
